What you need to know:  Nairobi County teams registered wins in handball, netball and basketball in both men and women categories to mark a good start to the GamesIn other women's basketball matches, hosts Kisumu County handed Kericho a humiliating 52-04 defeat while Uasin Gishu thrashed Embu 40-06In football, Kisii started off well with a 2-0 win over resilient Murang’a in a Pool 'D' match played at Kisumu National Polytechnic ground